                <h1>Professors from low-income first-generation backgrounds are ready to help Duke students</h1>
                
                                    <figure class="dom-art-container my-4">
                                                    <img src="https://snworksceo.imgix.net/dtc/78a67660-d9e6-4617-ac09-d2d56d3f8218.sized-1000x1000.jpg?w=1000" alt="&lt;p&gt;From&#x20;top&#x20;right,&#x20;going&#x20;clockwise&#x3A;&#x20;Kishor&#x20;Trivedi,&#x20;Terrie&#x20;Moffitt,&#x20;Jen&#x2019;nan&#x20;Read,&#x20;Kenneth&#x20;Brown&lt;&#x2F;p&gt;" class="w-100">
